  "description": {
    "de": "Ideal, um sich vor der Sonne, vor Vampiren oder vor neuen Bekanntschaften zu schützen.",
    "en": "This is the perfect staff for protecting yourself from the sun, and will prompt hours of ripe debate amongst your peers. Is it really a sunshade, or an umbrella?",
